{"tid":1640360,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"我吃了太子的高質糖水黃店-芋圓圓","createTime":"2019-10-09T02:33:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T00:38:03.000Z","uid":13361,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ff3b3de40443e8366ddf3b10ec67c08daa62a90c","tid":1640360,"uid":13361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:33:29.000Z","msg":"612 85罷工<br />\n<br />\n位置比較偏僻 兜左兩個圈先見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一入間鋪好大浸芋頭味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uHjmVmO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuHjmVmO.png&h=11df3cc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n試佢招牌（我自己覺得係招牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）仙草配芋圓啦$32 ★★★★★ <br />\n三隻色三隻味 黃薯&amp;紫薯&amp;芋頭 手工製&amp;百分百天然食材製作（門口個牌寫）好有味 同煙un 我覺得比起曾經九份食過既更令我印象深刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 另外一樣好出色嘅係啲仙草勁滑 未食過仙草咁滑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以前一直覺得同涼粉差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />兜糖水最大缺點係唔夠凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />建議好似台灣咁加啲刨冰 一定變120分 個人覺得糖水唔夠凍真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/106wyfQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F106wyfQ.png&h=8927859b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DrnfZVX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDrnfZVX.png&h=fa212880&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n焦糖白酒千層蛋糕 $38 ★★★★☆<br />\n個人好撚鍾意焦糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢蛋糕面頭成層都係焦糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啲cream係焦糖加酒味 都幾夾又不會甜到漏 <br />\n<br />\n總結：。雖然千層蛋糕唔係整得好靚 但味道好食 值回票價 不過比起千層蛋糕 仙草配芋圓更有驚喜 btw下次問下店員可唔可以幫我加啲冰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iUqUv3s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiUqUv3s.png&h=663f6b8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（網絡圖片）<br />\n所有糖水好似都會有芋圓 連千層蛋糕都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本人只會推介自己覺得唔錯嘅黃店 絕非打手 大家試完覺得真係唔錯 可以返黎呢度講返聲 幫手推介比手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n10月10聽日一齊爆買黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋日日戴口罩 越多人戴就越多人敢戴 多你一個都好多 剩係返工放工戴都得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dee918027609d057796de769915f6a6d52426e2","tid":1640360,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:33:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rG1sQ5b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrG1sQ5b.jpg&h=d6b3d577&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K9NvORS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK9NvORS.jpg&h=fcaaa2a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全球「和尼畫」#XinniethePooh Challenge<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1640322/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1640322/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n「和尼畫」挑戰<br />\n1.畫出你心中所想的維尼圖<br />\n2.留下你想對習維尼講嘅說話<br />\n3.放上ig、fb、twitter，tag #XinniethePooh<br />\n4.tag 1-3個你想佢一齊畫維尼嘅朋友<br />\n5.被tag嘅朋友一齊畫維尼，讓愛與維尼佔領地球，推到畀習維尼本人見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「Xinnie the Pooh」Challenge<br />\n1. Draw your own &quot;Xinnie the Pooh&quot;<br />\n2. Write down what do you want to tell Chairman Xi<br />\n3. Post your work on instagram, facebook and twitter with tag #Xinnie the Pooh<br />\n4. Tag up to 3 more friends to ask them draw together!<br />\n5. Those who are tagged also join to draw Xinnie the Pooh, keep drawing until Chairman Xi can see our works!!"},{"pid":"7e41d0ad2ff613e3e469fb624856a6b36efcf651","tid":1640360,"uid":34553,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:38:52.000Z","msg":"呢間唔錯<br />\n係間鋪細咗啲"},{"pid":"429afc253758adc7f86ed5591dfafb8122fe7d81","tid":1640360,"uid":13361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e41d0ad2ff613e3e469fb624856a6b36efcf651","tid":1640360,"uid":34553,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:38:52.000Z","msg":"呢間唔錯<br />\n係間鋪細咗啲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:39:52.000Z","msg":"間鋪都幾大喎 好似搬過<br />\n<br />\n芋圓圓<br />\r\n    <br />\r\n網址: <a href=\"https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0cQK900~ufMj9Ag\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.openrice.com%2FQrbS0cQK900~ufMj9Ag&d=h%2FIbyvsQTNyUi2WbZ%2BJFJ9Dxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=45a91e2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0cQK900~ufMj9Ag</a><br />\r\n地址: 太子柏樹街1號地舖<br />\r\n電話: 55430154<br />\r\n====================="},{"pid":"80ec1a911fdb700341a078e45669cb6dfc159153","tid":1640360,"uid":33539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:41:20.000Z","msg":"睇到流哂口水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df9e42427c5017ab250805599e63775c318ba2be","tid":1640360,"uid":212623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:43:54.000Z","msg":"想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f6c397f3e10154877484ad578b35c9233226da9","tid":1640360,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:48:04.000Z","msg":"懲罰都要有地址先得㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77d6781b39b6952274a16586a69e4abd3a00f9f5","tid":1640360,"uid":13361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f6c397f3e10154877484ad5